34 PART C
35 Sec. C-1. Attrition savings. Notwithstanding any provision of law to the contrary,
36 the attrition rate for the 2026-2027 biennium is increased from 1.6% to 5% for executive
37 branch departments and agencies only. The attrition rate for subsequent biennia is 1.6%.
38 Sec. C-2. Calculation and transfer. Notwithstanding any provision of law to the
39 contrary, the State Budget Officer shall calculate the amount of savings in this Part that
40 applies against each Highway Fund account for all departments and agencies from savings
41 associated with attrition in fiscal year 2025-26 and fiscal year 2026-27 and shall transfer
42 the amounts by financial order upon the approval of the Governor. These transfers are
43 considered adjustments to appropriations in fiscal year 2025-26 and fiscal year 2026-27.
